{"tid":2243793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉兆佳：在中央眼中  香港=國安威脅","createTime":"2020-10-15T04:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T02:03:30.000Z","uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"73abadeffd8406cca4368b0d5fd4523491242ebd","tid":2243793,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:11:48.000Z","msg":"劉兆佳：香港在中央眼中構成國安威脅 港人危機感不足<br />\n<br />\n全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳認為，香港在中央眼中已構成國家安全威脅，又認為香港人及特區政府的危機感都不足，強調若香港與內地不合作，將不利發展。中大經濟學系副教授莊太量表示，深圳本地生產總值超過香港屬必然，但認為深圳難以在金融方面取代香港。<br />\n<br />\n2020-10-15 12:07:03<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554875-20201015.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554875-20201015.htm&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyicv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=403e391e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554875-20201015.htm&h=5d37f447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554875-20201015.htm</a>"},{"pid":"598f99413d54ee014245c01a5e86ef3ba93a9329","tid":2243793,"uid":53026,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:12:49.000Z","msg":"咁就好似馬來西亞踢走新加坡咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800efd6d16510d7e20a61c37df50f6e4171f950e","tid":2243793,"uid":14918,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"598f99413d54ee014245c01a5e86ef3ba93a9329","tid":2243793,"uid":53026,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:12:49.000Z","msg":"咁就好似馬來西亞踢走新加坡咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"踢走香港<br />\n<